Anthony Natale https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anthony_Natale 0 Anthony Natale is an actor who has performed in many movies and television shows such as Jerry Maguire and Mr. Holland's Opus. He portrays Cameron Bledsoe on the ABC series Switched at Birth. He teaches American Sign Language and enjoys fixing up houses in his spare time.
